from the perspective of

85
00:04:36,009 --> 00:04:39,012
on-site engineer, Boisjoly.

86
00:04:39,012 --> 00:04:42,015
Certainly, to give a
comprehensive analysis of

87
00:04:42,015 --> 00:04:45,018
the case from science
historical

88
00:04:45,018 --> 00:04:48,021
and technological
viewpoints,

89
00:04:48,021 --> 00:04:51,024
closer examinations
on evidences

90
00:04:51,024 --> 00:04:54,027
